thread.title: All passengers, crew in Iran plane crash believed dead: airline spokesman

author: Reuters Editorial
title: All passengers, crew in Iran plane crash believed dead: airline spokesman
text:
DUBAI (Reuters) - All 66 passengers and crew on an Iranian plane that crashed in a mountainous area of central Iran on Sunday are believed to be dead, state television Quote: d the airline’s spokesman as saying.
“Aseman Airlines public relations head said that all on board are unfortunately dead,” the television reporter said, without elaborating on how he obtained the information.
Reporting by Dubai Newsroom; Editing by Susan Fenton
